Real Effect Display  

Traditional packaging is mostly gift boxes, paper boxes, plastic bags, etc. Although these types of packaging can protect products well, they cannot display the unique appearance characteristics of the product in the first instance. They cannot meet the increasing demands of consumers for differentiated packaging and enhanced product presentation. Transparent packaging boxes not only allow consumers to see the product at a glance to understand it, but also enhance their purchasing power.
src: 传统的包装盒多为铁盒，纸盒，塑料等包装，虽然这类包装盒也能很好的保护产品，但他们都不能第一时间的展现产品的外观和特点，更不能满足打造差异化包装和提升产品营销效果的要求，而透明包装盒除了可以让消费者第一时间看到产品，了解产品，还能提升消费者购买力。
